OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAfter a fine
OL,6,Fand sunny evening, a dry night will
OL,7,Ffollow with clear spells and light
OL,8,Fwinds. Feeling warm and muggy,
OL,9,Fespecially in the east, bringing
OL,10,Fdifficult sleeping conditions.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FMostly dry with sunny spells.
OL,13,FSome showers possible, these turning
OL,14,Fheavy with hail and thunder possible
OL,15,Fin the east late afternoon. Feeling
OL,16,Fhot and humid for all.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
