OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FRemaining dry and sunny throughout the
OL,7,Fperiod. Feeling hot by day in the
OL,8,Fstrong sunshine and increasingly warm
OL,9,Fand humid overnight.
